===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Flint (Masters)}}
Flint forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Flint|Infernape}} and {{p|Rapidash}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Flint became a playable sync pair since the game's release, with him joining the {{player}} after they complete the twelfth chapter of the [[PML arc]].

Flint has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the PML arc.

